og.title: null Democratic Vice Presidential Nominee Tim Kaine Delivers Remarks at Campaign Event in Fayetteville, N.C.
og.description: Hey guys. Great to be with you. Thank you. What a great group. I am so glad, I am so glad to be here in North Carolina, you are very important this year. You're very important. And I'm so glad to be here with Anne. Please have a seat.
